<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5019785>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–4. Abdominal segment 8 of Tinotus acerbus (Casey) (lectotype of Acrimea acerba (1–2) and lectotype of Acri. resecta (3–4)). 1 — male tergum 8; 2 — male sternum 8; 3 — female tergum 8; 4 — female sternum 8. Scale bar 0.2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5019785/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5019810>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31–35. Abdominal segment 8 of Atheta aemula (Erichson) (male (31–33) and female (34–35), 1.5–2.5 km N Lawrence, Kansas). 31 — male tergum 8; 32 — male sternum 8; 33 — apex of male tergum 8; 34 — female tergum 8; 35 — female sternum 8. Scale bar 0.2 mm (33), 0.4 mm (31–32, 34–35)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5019810/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

